===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|en|enm|ravene}}, {{m|enm|ravine}}, from {{der|en|fro|raviner|t=rush, seize by force}}, itself from {{m|fro|ravine|t=rapine}}, from {{der|en|la|rapƒ´na|t=plundering, loot}}, itself from {{m|la|rapere|t=seize, plunder, abduct}}.

