==English==
{{wikipedia|January}}

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|Januarie}}, {{m|enm|januari}}, re-latinised forms of {{cog|enm|Janevere}}, {{m|enm|Ieneuer}}, from {{der|en|xno|genever}}, from {{bor|en|la|iƒÅnuƒÅrius||(month) of [[Janus]]}}, perhaps from a {{der|en|ine-pro|*h‚ÇÅey-||to go|pos=a root}}. {{doublet|en|Gennaro}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|en|/ÀàdÕ° í√¶n.j( ä.)…ô.…πi/}} ''or as US''
* {{a|US}} {{enPR|jƒÉn πyoÕûo-ƒïr'ƒì}}, {{IPA|en|/ÀàdÕ° í√¶njuÀå…õ…πi/|/ÀàdÕ° í√¶njuÀå√¶…πi/}}
* {{a|AU}} {{IPA|en|/ÀàdÕ° í√¶nj âÀåeÀê…πi/|/ÀàdÕ° í√¶nj…ô…πi/|/ÀàdÕ° í√¶n…πi/}}
