==Danish==

===Etymology===
From {{bor|da|fr|marche}}, derived from the verb {{m|fr|marcher||to march}}, a Frankish loanword, ultimately from {{der|da|gem-pro|*mark≈çnƒÖ||to mark, notice}}. The interjection is borrowed form the French imperative of this verb.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|da|[Ààm…ëÀê…ï]}}

===Noun===
