Cognate with {{cog|nl|mag||may|pos=first and third-person singular of {{m|nl|mogen||to be able to, be allowed to, may}}}}, {{cog|nds|m√∂gen}}, {{cog|de|mag||like|pos=first and third-person singular of {{m|de|m√∂gen||to like, want, require}}}}, {{cog|sv|m√•}}, {{cog|is|mega}}, {{m|is|megum}}. See also {{m|en|might}}.

