From {{inh|en|enm|Julie}}, {{m|enm|julye}}, {{m|enm|iulius}}, from {{der|en|xno|julie}}, from {{der|en|fro|jule}}, {{m|fro|juil}}, from {{der|en|la|i≈´lius}} ({{w|Julius Caesar|Gaius Julius Caesar}}'s month), perhaps a contraction of ''*Iovilios'', "descended from [[Jove]]".

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|j…ô-lƒ´ π|joÕûo-|joÕùo-}}, {{IPA|en|/dÕ° í…ôÀàla…™/|/dÕ° íuÀêÀàla…™/|/dÕ° í äÀàla…™/}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-July.ogg|Audio (US)}}
