===Etymology 1===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*h‚ÇÇewg-}}
From {{der|en|fr|auguste||noble, stately; august}} or {{der|en|la|augustus||majestic, venerable, august; imperial, royal}},<ref>{{R:Lexico}}</ref> from {{m|la|auge≈ç||to augment, increase; to enlarge, expand, spread}}, ultimately from {{der|en|ine-pro|*h‚ÇÇewg-||to enlarge, increase}}. {{doublet|en|Augustus}}.

