===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|-}}, from late {{der|en|ang|-}}, from {{der|en|fro|septembre}}, {{der|en|la|september||seventh month}}, from {{m|la|septem||seven}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*sept·∏øÃ•||seven}}; + {{der|en|la|-ber}}, from {{m|la|-bris}}, an adjectival suffix; September was the seventh month in the Roman calendar.

