==English==
{{wikipedia|dab=wednesday (disambiguation)|wednesday}}

===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*d ∞eg ∑ ∞-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|Wednesday}}, {{m|enm|Wednesdai}}, {{m|enm|Wodnesdei}}, from {{inh|en|ang|w≈çdnesd√¶ƒ°||Wednesday}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*W≈çdanas dag}}, a calque ({{m|la|interpretƒÅti≈ç germƒÅnica}}) of {{der|en|la|diƒìs Mercuriƒ´||day of Mercury}} and Koine {{cog|grc|·º°ŒºŒ≠œÅŒ±||day}} {{m|grc|·ºôœÅŒºŒø·ø¶||of Hermes}}, via an association of the god {{m|en|Odin}} (Woden) with {{m|en|Mercury}} and {{m|en|Hermes}}.

Cognate with {{cog|fy|woansdei||Wednesday}}, {{cog|nl|woensdag||Wednesday}}, {{cog|nds-nl|woonsdag||Wednesday}}, dialectal {{cog|de|Wodenstag||Wednesday}}, {{cog|da|onsdag||Wednesday}}, {{cog|nb|onsdag||Wednesday}}, {{cog|sv|onsdag||Wednesday}}.

