===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*d ∞eg ∑ ∞-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|Saterday}}, from {{inh|en|ang|s√¶terd√¶g}}, earlier {{m|ang|s√¶ternesd√¶ƒ°||day of Saturn}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*SƒÅturnas dag}}; a translation of {{der|en|la|diƒìs Saturnƒ´}}. Compare {{cog|fy|saterdei}}, {{cog|nds-de|Saterdag}}, {{cog|nl|zaterdag}}.

===Pronunciation===
