# {{lb|en|linguistics|translation studies|lexicography}} A [[word]] in a language that bears a [[deceptive]] resemblance to a word in another language but in fact has a different meaning.
#: {{ux|en|A word and its '''false friend''' may well be etymologically related: in such cases semantic shifts have made them drift apart.}}
