===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of several large carnivorous and [[carrion]]-eating [[bird]]s in the family [[Accipitridae]], having a powerful [[hooked]] [[bill]] and [[keen]] [[vision]].
#: {{syn|en|erne|broadwing}}
# {{lb|en|US|numismatics|historical}} A [[gold]] [[coin]] with a face value of ten dollars, formerly used in the United States.
# {{lb|en|historical|numismatics}} A 13th-[[century]] [[coin]] [[mint]]ed in [[Europe]] and [[circulate]]d in [[England]] as a [[debase]]d [[sterling]] [[silver]] [[penny]], [[outlaw]]ed under {{w|Edward I of England}}.
# {{lb|en|golf}} A score of [[two]] [[under par]] for a [[hole]].

