# {{senseid|nn|solf√®ge}} {{lb|nn|music}} {{l|en|fa|id=solf√®ge}}, a syllable used in [[solf√®ge]] to represent the second note of a [[major scale]].

====Coordinate terms====
* {{sense|scale of solf√®ge}} ''{{l|nn|do|id=solf√®ge}}, {{l|nn|re|id=solf√®ge}}, {{l|nn|mi|id=solf√®ge}}, fa, {{l|nn|sol|id=solf√®ge}} or {{l|nn|so|id=solf√®ge}}, {{l|nn|la|id=solf√®ge}}, {{l|nn|ti|id=solf√®ge}}, {{l|nn|do|id=solf√®ge}}''

