{{also|aard-vark}}
==English==
[[Image:Erdferkel-drawing.jpg|thumb|right|Two aardvarks]]
{{wikipedia}}
{{wikispecies|Orycteropus afer}}

===Alternative forms===
* {{l|en|aard-vark}}, {{l|en|erdvark}}

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|af|aardvark}} {{qualifier|obsolete}}, {{m|af|erdvark}}, from {{m|af|aarde|t=earth}}, (from {{der|en|nl|-}}, from {{der|en|dum|aerde}}) + {{m|af|vark|t=pig}}, (from {{der|en|dum|varken}}). Early European colonists in South Africa noticed that the animal was similar to a pig, while "aarde" hints at the animal's habit of burrowing.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|en|/Àà…ëÀêd.v…ëÀêk/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/Àà…ë…πd.v…ë…πk/}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-aardvark.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[nocturnal]], [[insectivorous]], burrowing, [[mammal]] ''[[Orycteropus afer]]'', of the order [[Tubulidentata]], somewhat resembling a [[pig]], common in some parts of sub-Saharan Africa. {{defdate|from late 18<sup>th</sup> c.}}
#: {{syn|en|African anteater|antbear|ant bear|anteater|earth pig}}
#: {{ux|en|The '''aardvark''' burrows in the ground and feeds mostly on termites, which it catches with its long, slimy tongue.}}
# {{lb|en|slang|particularly in the southeast|_|US}} A [[silly]] or [[credulous]] person who is prone to [[mistake]]s or [[blunder]]s.
#: {{syn|en|fool}}
#: {{ux|en|I walked into the wrong bathroom like a total '''aardvark'''.}}
#: {{rfquote-sense|en}}

